Product Title: Fruit of the Loom Recover Cotton T-Shirt Made with Sustainable, Low Impact Recycled Fiber
Product Details: We are committed to a more Fruitful Future. In doing so we are big on turning things into other things! So, we partnered with Recover™ to create our Fruit of the Loom Recover™ Cotton T-shirt. This T-shirt is made with 20% Recover™ cotton, a high-quality, low-impact recycled fiber made from cotton textile waste. Recover™ cotton fiber production also uses less water compared to conventional cotton, so much that 1lb of Recover™ cotton saves up to approximately 114 showers or 6 years of drinking water*! This unisex cotton t-shirt provides more than just saving Earth – it’s made to last with double-needle stitching for extra re-enforcement. The shoulder-to-shoulder cover seam tape ensures your comfort. This sustainable t-shirt is a must-have for your drawer and as always, we provide the best fit, guaranteed! * Calculated using an LCA study verified by AITEX, Universitat de Valencia and UNESCO.
